Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:03.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.\NThe shoes. Shoes. Remove the shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:06.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I said remove the shoes\NOk..ok..ok
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:09.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You also. Remove the shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:14.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That looks delicious~\NAh! That's my crepe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:17.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes~\NWhat about when that time comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:22.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For my funeral, I absolutely don't want anything on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:26.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like retouching with powder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:30.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I don't want my face painted white when I turn 94
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:34.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys must not put anything to my face when that time comes! Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about make-up?\NI hate that also. I hate that more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:43.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,First of, take out the dullness off my face by using cream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:46.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm always using cream. So just apply a little bit of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:50.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Kyuto is not here..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:54.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder will I go hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:59.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to eat well
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:02.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! By the way Heita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Isao said that I'll give this to you.\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:07.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that this was the book you liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:09.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! This brings back the memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:14.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,“Just like men and organ. The Hippopotamus was able to produce a sound”.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:22.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:24.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,N..nothing. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:27.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok. Thank him by sending email
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:29.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Let's eat then!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:47.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((That's why I'm telling you, she isn't your belonging))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:05.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Q10 belongs to us))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:21.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that I'll come to school daily
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:24.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:28.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I'm able to see Fukai-kun everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:32.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I annoy you?\NI don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:40.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is I want you to go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:47.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no fun at all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:50.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're reaction is definitely boring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:58.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm liking you more when you are upset
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:21.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujino is sick and she's resting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really concerned about her. I'm supposed to go and visit her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:27.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it when you're getting depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was not talking about what happens to Fujino.\NI am talking about Kyuto and Fujino Tsukiko
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Don't talk about me to other people))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:40.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((If you do, I'm going to withdraw Q10 from you))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened between Fujino Tsukiko and Q10?\NWell..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, from now on..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If Fujino Tsukiko says something, tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you hate her for no reason...\NI hate her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:56.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like Fujino Tsukiko\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeezz grow up a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Since, I am a Tsukiko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:22.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,call me Runa-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:28.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwaa~~ Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:36.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This school is interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:41.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You might want to have the lucky bag this New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:44.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have packed a lot of things in that bag with effort
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:48.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing such things is what makes it enjoyable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you apply something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:57.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Smells like medicine...no..it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:02.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My skin is weak. I applied an important topical cream
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:15.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just like men and organ, the hippopotamus was able to produce a sound"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual that men and organ can be compared to hippopotamus' sound..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:22.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody wanted to have that one. That is why everybody is fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:26.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, nobody was able to get it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the story goes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:33.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"For Kenta, he folded the hippopotamus organ into a shape of a bag"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:37.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just like the suitcase, then he hurriedly escaped"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:44.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,“He was successful. He was successful”.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:48.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's the end?\NWhoa~ You're right
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? The problem was not solved
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But he escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't stop if he continues to ran away...\NLater on, for sure somebody will come after him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:58.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, someone has decided to bring it back...\NIf that happens, then he has to escape again
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:01.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so he keeps doing that, there will be another one who will get it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:05.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, he has to escape again\NNo...even though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:15.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:18.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the one who has the guts wins the fight right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:34.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Do you know which way is Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:37.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... eh? Osaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, its there in the West
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:46.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\NEh? Eh? You'll really go there? By that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh~~?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:56.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If we have to follow this familiar road ..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:59.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I really have no idea where it will lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:06.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,(( I have decided that I'll come to school everyday))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:10.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,(( Q10 belongs to us ))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:19.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have the guts to do it. For sure we'll be able to get there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:24.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:35.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:54.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm able to do it, I won't feel uneasy anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:35.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:39.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the most important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing?\NEh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:45.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that thing that I'm supposed to be looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:48.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what are you looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the most important for you sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... what could it be..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:55.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it will be difficult for me if this disappears...\NThis phone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:09:00.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Cellphones are convenient.\NOk. I know that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Convenient!\NThe way you use it is completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Tell her that's weird
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the boss here. It's better if you're the one saying
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:16.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem.\NCellphone has a lot of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be a chair\NYup. Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:27.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that is not how you use it.\NQ-chan, the most important thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Memory of family
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:34.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show her something that is biased...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:36.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have I been biased?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell her about general things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:42.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what is the most important thing to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:49.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwaah! That's disgusting! right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:52.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Gefu.\NGefu? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:58.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. These are 90 pieces of willows
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:03.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Give this as hospitality gift to the owner of the lodge you are going to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll...\NWhat is that baggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going for a sleep over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:37.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sleeping over to that good friend of yours?\NYes of course
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:40.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I have to go.\NOk~~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:44.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey! Come here..\NEh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:59.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For quite some time, I have always hidden this for the sake of someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:03.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"The dull life" No.1 manga
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:08.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In page 78, an unlikely event happens.\N"Seven tumbles, eight occurs"\N("Seven tumbles, eight occurs": is a proverb that means rising after a fall")
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?\NI understand what everyone is trying to say
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:16.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For them, a man should not say "Do you have something that I can spend?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:25.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:28.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's money\NYou don't know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:32.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NThat's 10,000 yen bill...You really don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:41.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to change clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing uniform makes us stand out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:50.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to give this 90 pcs willow as a hospitality gift
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:54.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. I'll pass it to them\NThen, we won't be found out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:57.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome if we'll be found out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:12:00.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret that we went out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:06.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the place for us to go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:11.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we will be successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I think that will be impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's impossible for me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a place where Kyuto can hide and won't be found out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:30.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I don't know for how long you must hide
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:33.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, one thing is for sure, I will definitely pick you up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:41.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By all means, I will definitely find a way that you'll be in front of me always
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:47.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make promises
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:53.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, I believe in Heita
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:26.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?　What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:29.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:32.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh..well..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:37.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you agree to my decision\NYup..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last time, I want to make a movie..\NKawai's movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, I'll stop from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:53.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But. I want to take this chance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm not cool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:02.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm slowly becoming worst\NBut I have high regard to the 3 of us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:04.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I want to take this chance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:21.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you at least make a movie that has happy moments?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:24.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to watch something like "We were going so well"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"We were so happy!"\NSomething like that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:39.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok. Sure. Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok~~ Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,“For the sake of the baby, eat a lot ok?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:57.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,“Yup. Delicious~”.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:00.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,“Ah! Look! There's a cream…”.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:10.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well ~ that's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,W..wait! What are you doing?! Jezz!\NSorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:25.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Don't do that! That stairs is dangerous for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:28.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's dangerous, I have to carry you then
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Carry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,W..wait! I'm heavy! You can't carry me!\NIt's ok! It's ok! You're not heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to fall! We're falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut! Cut! Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!\NLet's do again the stairs scene
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:44.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,a child is already born! Look~~\NNext, we'll do it properly! ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:46.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shotgun wedding?\NYou have a loud voice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:49.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything.\NCongratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not happy about it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:57.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But...\NSomehow, I'm a nasty person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:00.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would my daughter go to that kind of man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can do about forced marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she said when she gives birth
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:09.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,she will really try hard to hide her embarrassment. She hated that feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! I don't understand the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:14.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when will she give birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's either today or tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!\NAren't you going to her now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:21.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like celebrating with them but It'll be ok right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...I detest it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:27.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,W..wait...Principal! Principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:41.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:45.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For the meantime, over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:51.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Suitcase!\NSuitcase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:56.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Suitcase!\NSuitcase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:17:02.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a woman who's carrying a lot of baggage
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto is even a woman right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:29.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Water!　Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sea! Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:35.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwa! Uwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:38.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea ~!\NYou'll get wet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring that with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:47.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am waiting for the most important thing to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like what you said
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...I did say that but why album?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, who owns this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:58.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa sensei's grandmother\NIs that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it. I don't know her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:03.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~ This is funny. This album
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:06.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the person who gave birth to this person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is this person's older sister
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:13.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This onesan gave birth to this child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:16.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:19.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually people will die
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you Heita, will die, but the children are left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:25.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Children?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:38.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:40.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dead
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dead
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:04.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alive\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:11.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:14.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:18.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright\NDon't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm going to charge you now ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:28.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me~\NYes~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I use your source of electricity?\NOk.. Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the charger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to bring it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you said that I have to bring only the most important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:04.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah I said that, but that one is important right?\NThat charger is important right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:06.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You didn't bring it?\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:09.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh~~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:14.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Y..you really have done it...\NEhhh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:36.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:42.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good!\NHai
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:46.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...here..\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:49.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time that I baked.\NIt's a bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:53.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You really baked this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:58.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:01.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time when you gave us bread, I wasn't able to pull it well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:05.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Share it among yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:09.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I want to make something warm..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:14.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh~~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:18.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! What are you doing?\NGet out from there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeezz
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:35.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of tomorrow~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:45.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Pan? Oh! Pan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:50.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the first bread that Fujioka baked
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:55.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to smell the scent of tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:09.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, Yamakawa-san is going to take care of his family
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:15.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He will devote his life doing that.\NHe is retiring from work right now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:19.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well aside from that news,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:23.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a new worker that will work hard from now on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:26.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Depression is far from over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:29.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to work together! Let's do our best!\NCheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:31.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:36.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:38.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:41.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:53.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto is sleepy now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:58.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwa~~ w..wai..wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:03.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They're madly in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:05.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so madly in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:08.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:23.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for me to take you back home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:28.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only place we can go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:36.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry..I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:55.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma is here~~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:59.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and come out already~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.68,0:24:03.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wait for you~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:08.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, here is your grandchild~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:11.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Babu babu babu babu..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:14.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama~ Mama~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:17.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-in law!\NMom!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:20.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to die~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:24.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Dried frozen tofu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.16,0:24:28.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Soak it in water...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.18,0:24:32.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,haaaahh... there...fore...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.66,0:24:44.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it\NOk! Cut! Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.64,0:24:47.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.16,0:24:49.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.25,0:24:56.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye! bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.17,0:24:59.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.66,0:25:09.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...what will I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.67,0:25:28.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.15,0:25:30.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well….
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.67,0:25:35.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That one is not working\NNobody is using that one
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:39.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That was not used for so many years\NIt's terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.77,0:25:42.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to ride a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.67,0:25:47.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask somebody over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:26:00.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.77,0:26:04.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Today isn't over yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.16,0:26:08.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like at home or in school..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.65,0:26:12.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.67,0:26:21.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.66,0:26:26.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt that I wanted to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.67,0:26:31.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto cannot go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.85,0:27:46.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise. I'm going to see you again
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.67,0:27:50.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make promises
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.69,0:27:56.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, I always believe in Heita
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.65,0:27:59.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.67,0:28:05.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto doesn't like promises
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.82,0:29:59.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call Dr. Suzuki!\NOk!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.34,0:30:01.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,7-8-9-10!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.32,0:30:03.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Give epinephrine!\NHai!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.87,0:30:17.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'll go home now
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.85,0:30:26.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.82,0:30:35.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawatani-san, the doctor wanted to talk to you.\NThis way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.84,0:30:37.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah..ok
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.83,0:30:46.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What the doctor is about to say is..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.82,0:30:50.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,“This is the last time that you can see the patient.\NThis is the time you'll be together.."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.84,0:30:55.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"But, during that time that he's brain dead.\NWill it be ok for you if we remove the the machine that supports him"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.83,0:30:59.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He's about to say like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.40,0:31:02.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless already
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.84,0:31:06.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.83,0:31:13.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.31,0:31:17.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the person who I have occasionally talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.87,0:31:21.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,“It's just like working out"..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.32,0:31:25.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He's carrying the IV stand as he climbs the stairs up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.83,0:31:28.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Don't tell the doctor about this ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.83,0:31:32.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand his feelings. I can't believe that he died
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.33,0:31:37.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back to Shaba as soon as possible.\NI want to walk to that bridge again
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.42,0:31:43.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We make bridges. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.34,0:31:45.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh~
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.83,0:31:50.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not married and I don't have children.\NBut here I am making bridges.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.85,0:31:54.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good? To have this kind of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.39,0:31:58.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever~ This guy right here is good as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.34,0:32:03.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes you are
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.33,0:32:05.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.33,0:32:07.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the last words that I heard from him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.32,0:32:12.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,“Whatever~"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.39,0:32:17.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"This guy here is good as it is"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.34,0:33:22.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.33,0:33:49.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.82,0:33:57.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Is there anyone out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.34,0:34:13.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being late!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.83,0:34:16.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the event for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.83,0:34:19.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I understand! That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.32,0:34:22.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I say something first?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.84,0:34:25.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.35,0:34:29.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to say a story that happened when I was still a student
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.43,0:34:33.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In our neighborhood, there is a rumor that happened at night
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.85,0:34:37.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.32,0:34:39.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a candle in a bread (pan)?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.84,0:34:43.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it doesn't matter whether its on a cake or a pan
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.84,0:34:45.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Aa.. eh? Then..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.84,0:34:48.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is like putting a candle on a real cake, right?\NYup
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.88,0:34:50.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.93,0:34:56.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is it perhaps, today's event is your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.34,0:34:59.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Today is my birthday~
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.34,0:35:02.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Why didn't you tell me beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.34,0:35:04.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have prepared a present for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.83,0:35:06.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your gift for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.85,0:35:11.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? A~ Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.37,0:35:15.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Necklace or flowers perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.84,0:35:17.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Aa..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.82,0:35:20.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want is...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.34,0:35:21.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.35,0:35:25.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A word.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.33,0:35:27.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Word??
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.84,0:35:38.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you write down for me? Words.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.34,0:35:39.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Haa
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.32,0:35:49.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're daughter will give birth to a child
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.36,0:35:53.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a destiny wherein you will have a deep connection with
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.83,0:35:55.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.83,0:36:01.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You got married twice right?\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.83,0:36:07.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're first wife was sick. Hence she died at young age!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.32,0:36:10.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.39,0:36:13.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the child that you're recent wife gave birth to..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.33,0:36:17.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She will give birth to a child that is the reincarnation of your first wife
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.35,0:36:19.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.84,0:36:24.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A reincarnation of Mitsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.38,0:36:32.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.35,0:36:40.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy?\NYes! I'm very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.84,0:36:42.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.. I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.34,0:36:45.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the one.. Here's the one..\NThat's not the one..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.34,0:36:48.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Henshin Reset"\NThis is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.85,0:36:53.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in elementary, I thought that was a gag! Gag!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.92,0:36:56.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words... "Hen..shin! reset!"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.82,0:36:59.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I want to transform ..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.34,0:37:01.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I eventually went back to the way I was and\NI noticed that nothing is changed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.84,0:37:04.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you say "reset" that happens for about 0.2 second..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.83,0:37:07.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then will transform back where everyone can't see it with their own eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.33,0:37:10.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I guess so..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.34,0:37:15.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Henshin...risetto (reset)
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.42,0:37:17.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!\NIs it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.83,0:37:19.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.33,0:37:27.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I give her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.82,0:37:32.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My life right now is just like a continuation of a drama series
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.81,0:37:40.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to me~~
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.34,0:38:38.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.33,0:38:44.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.90,0:38:48.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we're going to collect Q10 back?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.32,0:38:55.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.\NThe preparation for withdrawal will start tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.83,0:39:17.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My mission has ended
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.33,0:39:19.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
