Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.87,0:40:18.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That light is nostalgic,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.84,0:40:25.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen that light before I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.83,0:40:30.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,< It was a warm and gentle light >
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.85,0:40:38.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Aahh~ Nice meeting you\NI'm your grandfather~
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.39,0:40:43.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who are waiting to that place where I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.83,0:40:45.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A~ he's lively!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.83,0:40:50.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back to that place I was before.
